# Design Responsive Mobile-First

## Principe Fondamental

> **Mobile: p-2 → Desktop (md+): p-4**

## Breakpoints Tailwind

| Breakpoint | Taille | Usage |
|------------|--------|-------|
| `sm` | 640px+ | Petites tablettes |
| `md` | 768px+ | **Point de bascule principal** |
| `lg` | 1024px+ | Desktop |

## Conventions d'Espacement

```tsx
// ✅ CORRECT - Mobile first
className="p-2 md:p-4"
className="gap-2 md:gap-4"

// ❌ INCORRECT - Pas responsive
className="p-4"
```

## Headers Responsifs

```tsx
<h1 className="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold">Événements</h1>
<p className="text-muted-foreground hidden sm:block">
  Gérez vos événements et diffusions
</p>
```

## Filtres Compacts (Icône Mobile)

```tsx
<SelectTrigger className="w-10 sm:w-[160px] h-9 px-2 sm:px-3">
  <Filter className="h-4 w-4 sm:hidden" />
  <span className="hidden sm:inline">
    <SelectValue placeholder="Statut" />
  </span>
</SelectTrigger>
```

## Boutons Action

```tsx
<Button className="h-9 w-9 sm:w-auto sm:px-4 shrink-0">
  <Plus className="h-4 w-4 sm:mr-2" />
  <span className="hidden sm:inline">Nouvel événement</span>
</Button>
```

## Sidebar Responsive (3 modes)

| Taille | Breakpoint | Mode |
|--------|------------|------|
| Desktop | ≥1024px | Expanded (texte + icônes) |
| Tablet | 768-1023px | Collapsed (icônes seules) |
| Mobile | <768px | Offcanvas (sheet) |
